{"tid":1566490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲又追擊港台！一人一信還港台一個公道","createTime":"2019-09-13T15:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T01:30:52.000Z","uid":220977,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0be17330e9220bbddf9c41aa1494603aa76b4644","tid":1566490,"uid":220977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T15:14:36.000Z","msg":"救命呀！繼之前香港政研發起萬人包圍港台，誣蔑港台偏幫示威者，hkgpao又搞左個聯署搞港台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeiWLHx7Ao-IsJrBjFq1xNtLjCnPHXWyoSAJqmaTmHdZMN32w/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSeiWLHx7Ao-IsJrBjFq1xNtLjCnPHXWyoSAJqmaTmHdZMN32w%2Fviewform&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88jizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=2637d4f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeiWLHx7Ao-IsJrBjFq1xNtLjCnPHXWyoSAJqmaTmHdZMN32w/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n唔該大家幫手拉到<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">最低report呢個google form</span></strong> - 檢舉濫用情形 &mdash;&gt; 煽動仇恨、暴力或違法/無禮行為<br />\n<br />\n====================================<br />\n<br />\n我真係好嬲呀，港台係一個公正持平既傳媒黎架嗎，我地要還港台一個公道!<br />\n<br />\n之前原由柏実巴打提議 - 我地不如<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一人一信去通訊局表揚港台</span></strong>一直用<strong>不偏不倚,專業,用心既態度製作節目，多謝佢地謹守崗位，堅持報道真相</strong>！<br />\n<br />\n通訊局得投訴電郵無表揚電郵<br />\n依個係佢地有關廣播事務既聯絡電郵:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; webmaster@ofca.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n亦可以send埋俾港台：<br />\n香港電台機構傳訊組:&nbsp;ccu@rthk.hk<br />\n<br />\n內容記得講明睇開港台31 定32台，最like咩節目同點解<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家寫返自己嘅意見出嚟，短短地都得㗎啦，唔需要好文筆，一模一樣既信有機會俾佢地當做同一封信！港台咁多好節目唔會太難寫！<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該唔好寫到佢地偏幫示威者咁。佢地唔係呀！佢地只係報道緊真相</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢個未必係最好既方法，大家有橋請提議！<br />\n<br />\n最後最重要都係大家長開31，32台，下載晒佢地d apps, 提曬佢地既youtube片<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef35bb54bf96909568452fd8e1f1cb364690c24","tid":1566490,"uid":123713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T15:15:17.000Z","msg":"[國際戰線] 香港人唔可以當其他國家係Condom!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1565130</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/thrHTWT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FthrHTWT.jpg&h=21d791c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9bd889cf638cd5682b5b1db405e0eb031b76371b","tid":1566490,"uid":220977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T15:15:27.000Z","msg":"還港台一個公道"},{"pid":"cfd4c14b48fcc643f7a3bf5c60089aff0f01cd60","tid":1566490,"uid":220977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T15:17:02.000Z","msg":"我諗住寫：<br />\n我是香港電台31台,32台的觀眾. 特此表揚港台一直為香港市民製作專業節目，擴闊市民的視野. 視點31經常請來不同背景的嘉賓，為觀眾提供多角度的分析; 鏗鏘集：721元朗黑夜嘗試重組7月21日元朗發生什麼事,令大眾可以多接近一點真相; 香港電台新聞秉持最高的新聞專業標準, 提供準確而持平的新聞報道. 另外, 香港電台亦不斷推陳出新, 節目內容與時並進, 例如開創香港首個學術清談節目《五夜講場》,給予大眾一個新平台吸納新知識."},{"pid":"85498e38f38a695a8bc45d2914b66ca0fd3f3f99","tid":1566490,"uid":220977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T15:17:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d3d52d2f4cc7bf3dc03ed0b9fd06f05b21e17f38","tid":1566490,"uid":320290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T15:17:30.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nReported"},{"pid":"8abef2e91c6a57b844c67dd97345876d5277b24b","tid":1566490,"uid":220977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T15:17:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02a528e33ad078354732b0d742331c6dd9521543","tid":1566490,"uid":220977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3d52d2f4cc7bf3dc03ed0b9fd06f05b21e17f38","tid":1566490,"uid":320290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T15:17:30.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nReported"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019